'''國際電子元件會議'''（{{lang-en|'''International Electron Devices Meeting'''}}，縮寫：'''IEDM'''），是每年12月在美國[[舊金山|舊金山]]或[[華盛頓哥倫比亞特區|華盛頓哥倫比亞特區]]其中一處舉行的年度電子會議。此會議作為一個論壇，在其中報告[[半導體|半導體]]、電子元件技術、設計、製造、物理與模型等領域中的技術突破。<ref>{{cite news | first = Nicolas | last = Mokhoff | title = Start of a beautiful friendship | date = 18 Dec 2006 | publisher = UBM Tech | url = http://www.eetimes.com/electronics-news/4067782/Start-of-a-beautiful-friendship | work = EE Times | accessdate = 2013-04-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = Nicolas | last = Mokhoff | title = Nanotechnology, organics advance toward IEDM | date = 6 Oct 2000 | publisher = UBM Tech | url = http://www.eetimes.com/electronics-news/4041053/Nanotechnology-organics-advance-toward-IEDM | work = EE Times | accessdate = 2013-04-25}}</ref>'''IEDM'''將世界上工業界與學界的管理者、工程師和科學家聚在一起討論奈米級[[CMOS|CMOS]]電晶體技術、先進記憶體、顯示、感測器、[[微機電系統|微機電系統]]元件、新穎量子與{{tsl|en|nanoscale|奈米級規模}}元件、[[粒子物理學現象|粒子物理學現象]]、[[光電工程|光電工程]]、功率與{{tsl|en|energy harvesting|能量收集元件}}、高速元件、製程技術、元件模型化與模擬。
會議也涵蓋[[矽|矽]]、[[化合物半導體|化合物]]、[[有機半導體|有機]]半導體與新興材料系統元件的討論和簡報。<ref>{{cite news | first = Nicolas | last = Mokhoff | title = Compound semiconductors hot topic at IEDM | date =2011-09-20| publisher = UBM Tech | url = http://www.eetimes.com/electronics-news/4227725/Compound-semiconductors-hot-topic-at-IEDM | work = EE Times | accessdate = 2013-04-25 | archive-date = 2011-12-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111224083713/http://www.eetimes.com/electronics-news/4227725/Compound-semiconductors-hot-topic-at-IEDM | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = Gail | last = Purvis | title = IEDM, where the device is king | date = 15 Nov 2012 | url = http://www.powersystemsdesign.com/iedm-where-the-device-is-king?a=1&c=1151 | work = Power Systems Design | accessdate = 2013-04-25 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130606220511/http://www.powersystemsdesign.com/iedm-where-the-device-is-king?a=1&c=1151 | archivedate = 2013-06-06 }}</ref>除技術論文簡報外，IEDM包含多個全體簡報、小組會議、教程、短期課程與由工業界與學界專家所引導的邀請會談。<ref>{{cite news | first = Robert | last = Haavlind | title = IEDM shows real details of materials technology, devices | date = 1 Jan 2008 | publisher = Penwell Corporation | url = http://www.electroiq.com/articles/sst/print/volume-51/issue-1/departments/iedm-report/iedm-shows-real-details-of-materials-technology-devices.html | work = Solid State Technology | accessdate = 2013-04-25 }}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = Pieter | last = Burggraaf | title = IEDM 1999 focused on CMOS solutions | date = 1 Feb 2000 | publisher = PennWell Corporation | url = http://www.electroiq.com/articles/sst/print/volume-43/issue-2/departments/world-news/iedm-1999-focused-on-cmos-solutions.html | work = Solid State Technology | accessdate = 2013-04-25 }}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = Mark | last = Lapedus | title = Update - IEDM: Papers down, challenges up | date = 10 Dec 2010 | publisher = UBM Tech | url = http://www.eetimes.com/electronics-news/4211425/IEMD--Papers-down--challenges-up | work = EE Times | accessdate = 2013-04-25 | archive-date = 2011-05-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110511044734/http://www.eetimes.com/electronics-news/4211425/IEMD--Papers-down--challenges-up | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 贊助發起 ==
國際電子元件會議是由[http://www.ieee.org/ 電機電子工程師學會]{{Wayback|url=http://www.ieee.org/ |date=20180405001450 }}(IEEE)中的[http://eds.ieee.org/ 電子元件學會] {{Wayback|url=http://eds.ieee.org/ |date=20210110142444 }}(EDS)所贊助發起的。

== 歷史 ==
第一屆年度電子元件技術會議(於1960年代中期更名為國際電子元件會議)於1955年10月24-25日在華盛頓哥倫比亞特區的{{tsl|en|Shoreham Hotel|索爾海姆酒店}}舉行，大約有700位科學家參與。
在那時候，七歲大的電晶體與[[真空管|真空管]]為電子元件的主要技術。發表了國家最先進電子元件技術的54篇論文，主要來自四家美國公司：[[貝爾實驗室|貝爾實驗室]]、[[美國無線電公司|美國無線電公司]]、[[休斯飛機公司|休斯飛機公司]]和{{tsl|en|Sylvania Electric Products|西爾瓦尼亞電子產品}}。
兩個主要的原因驅動了電子元件會議的需要，其一是快速成長的新興"[[固態電子器件|固態]]"電子分支，另一個則是美國政府[[航空太空|航空太空]]和防衛中對於固態[[電子元件|電子元件]]與更好[[微波|微波]]管的渴望。<ref>{{cite journal | title = A production model K-band backward wave oscillator | journal = IRE Transactions on Electron Devices | date = April 1956 | first = A.W. | last = McEwan | volume = 3 | issue = 2 | pages = 108 | doi = 10.1109/T-ED.1956.14115 | url = http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/login.jsp?tp=&arnumber=1472034&url=http%3A%2F%2Fieeexplore.ieee.org%2Fiel5%2F16%2F31547%2F01472034 | accessdate = 2013-04-25 | archive-date = 2014-04-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140419012030/http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/login.jsp?tp=&arnumber=1472034&url=http%3A%2F%2Fieeexplore.ieee.org%2Fiel5%2F16%2F31547%2F01472034 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

